Congressional Reports: Committed to the Committee of the Whole House on the State of the Union and ordered to be printed

The Committee on Resources, to whom was referred the bill (H.R. 2392) to amend the Umatilla Basin Project Act to establish boundaries for irrigation districts within the Umatilla Basin, and for other purposes, having considered the same, report favorably thereon with an amendment and recommend that the bill as amended do pass.
